comments: Very funny and nice teacher. Laid back and knowledgeable about the subject. Not always very clear, although she tries, and at times went in to too much unnecessary detail. Very approachable, and you definitley get the sense that she wants everyone to do well. Also understanding.
She is a skillful lecturer who challenges her students and is passionate and very knowledgable about her subject. Also attractive, as appealing as the TA.
She is light-hearted and easy going. The class environment is comfortable as opposed to intimidating. Professor Kat\'s note are helpful following her lectures.
She is very knowledgable, extremely extremely helpful, and very fun. Excellent teacher. Marks fairly easily as well. Pretty cute too ;)
